Through a search carried out on the Pubmed platform, an increase in the number of articles published with the keyword mHealth was observed, from 2,284 articles in 2014 to 8,012 in 2024 (
Figure 1
). The search carried out with the keywords mobile application, and hypertension resulted in 9 articles published in 2014 and 92 in 2024 (
Figure 2
), but of these, only 3 were also published in Portuguese, which demonstrates that few studies have been carried out with the Brazilian population.
